<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ku">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>مەکە</title>

<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: sans-serif;
  background: #f5f5f5;
  text-align: center;
}

.header {
  background: #0f5132;
  color: white;
  padding: 15px;
  font-size: 20px;
}

.card {
  background: white;
  margin: 15px;
  border-radius: 15px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  overflow: hidden;
}

.card img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 180px;
  object-fit: cover;
}

.card h2 {
  padding: 10px;
}

.btn {
  display: inline-block;
  margin: 10px;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  background: #198754;
  color: white;
  border-radius: 10px;
  text-decoration: none;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="header">هۆتێلەکانی مەکە 🕌</div>

<div class="card">
  <img src="hero.jpg">
  <h2>هۆتێلی نزیک کعبە</h2>
</div>

<div class="card">
  <img src="info.jpg">
  <h2>هۆتێلی بە نرخێکی باش</h2>
</div>

<a class="btn" href="index.html">گەڕانەوە</a>

</body>
</html>
